name: GIFT CERTIFICATE
description:
You wanna give a lover, friend, family member or relative the most awesome present ever?

Don't look any further! 

Our gift certificates are starting at €10,00 and go all the way up to €1.000,00! 
So you can give that special person a beanie, or 60 beanies! It's up to you! 



* the gifted person must spend the amount that stated on the gift card at once, and spend as much as stated on the card to make the code work. Excluded shipping costs. 

* if you somehow guess the code before it's sold as a gift certificate, I'll keep the money, you cheap bastard!

name: FS&S NATURAL BEARD OIL - AUTUMN WARMTH - 10ML
description:
FELLOWS SLICKS AND STIFFENERS NATURAL BEARD OIL - AUTUMN WARMTH - 10ML 

Be you biker, metalhead, lumberjack or beard enthusiast our natural beard oils are for you. 
Our Autumn Warmth beard oil is a seasonal special which will change with the seasons and is only available for three months of the year.

Our beard oil is a complementary blend of 100% pure base oils and 100% pure essential oils with added natural multivitamins that promote hair growth, soften skin and hair, strengthen hair at the roots, moisturise skin and hair, prevent itchiness and ensure that the hair is bursting with life with its natural glory!

INGREDIENTS: 
Sweet Almond (pure), Cedarwood (essential oil), Blackpepper (essential oil), Rosewood (essential oil), Patchouli (essential oil), Vitamin e (pure)

NOTE: 
May contain trace of nuts. 
May contain trace of black pepper 
We suggest using a tiny drop on your skin as in some cases irritation can occur.


*THIS IS A PRE ORDER ITEM AND WILL NOT BE SHIPPED UNTIL 20/12/13. 
ANYTHING ELSE ORDERED WITH THIS PRODUCT WILL ALSO BE ON HOLD UNTIL THE SAID DATE. 
OVER SEAS CUSTOMERS MAY NOT RECEIVE THEIR ORDER UNTIL THE NEW YEAR.
